O'KELLY: Three kids
go into those woods,

00:17.017 --> 00:18.644
only one
comes out alive.

00:18.769 --> 00:21.563
You two, get across that Peter,
Germaine, and Adam case.

00:21.688 --> 00:23.106
Any detail,
any connection.

00:23.232 --> 00:25.859
| don't care how tiny
or random it is.

00:25.984 --> 00:26.985
Hound it down.

00:27.110 --> 00:29.112
Peter? Jamie?

00:29.238 --> 00:31.114
SHANE: Our evil.

00:31.240 --> 00:33.242
Ours. You, me and Jonathan,
the three of us.

00:33.367 --> 00:34.743
There's no escape.
We can't escape.

00:35.786 --> 00:37.621
Mr. Johnstone may
be in prison,

00:37.746 --> 00:39.164
but he has associates
to do the work for him.

00:39.248 --> 00:42.334
We can't do this.
Not this one.

00:42.459 --> 00:46.004
Say yes, Rob, because we
absolutely cannot do this one.

00:46.129 --> 00:49.341
- Adam! Adam! Where are they?
- JOHN: Leave him alone!

00:50.842 --> 00:52.636
ADAM: My middle name's Robert.

00:53.929 --> 00:55.180
